/* Sketch Garden Nanode.ino

 Sketch Garden is a service for uploading sketches to your Nanode over the internet instead of using
 an FTDI / Programming cable connected to your computer.

 This library allows a remote reset, so you can upload sketches to your device from any computer
  regardless of where your device is located.

 For use with http://sketchgarden.co
 This sketch is released into the public domain by 
 Wicked Device LLC
 Author: Vic Aprea, March 2012
